title: Lifetime-The Trials of Cate McCall [2014]
description:
Lifetime-The Trials of Cate McCall [2014]

Air Date: 5 March 2014

Summary: In order to be reinstated to the bar and recover custody of her daughter, a hotshot lawyer, now in recovery and on probation, must take on the appeal of a woman wrongfully convicted of murder.
